# Style Guide for Remote Server Terminal Interface

## Color Palette
- **Primary Background**: Black (#000000) - Creates a dark, minimalist base
- **Secondary Background**: Dark gray (#121212) - Used for containers and cards
- **Text Colors**: 
  - White (#FFFFFF) for primary text and headings
  - Light gray (#AAAAAA) for secondary text and descriptions
- **Accent Colors**: 
  - White with transparency for interactive elements (buttons, hover states)
  - No blue colors should be used anywhere in the interface

## Typography
- **Font Family**: Roboto Mono (monospace) exclusively throughout the interface
- **Font Weights**: 
  - 700 (Bold) for headings and buttons
  - 400 (Regular) for body text and descriptions
- **Text Transformations**:
  - UPPERCASE for all navigation items, headings, and buttons
  - Normal case for descriptive text and content
- **Letter Spacing**:
  - 2-3px for headings and titles
  - 1px for navigation and buttons
- **Font Sizes**:
  - Large headings: 2.5rem (40px)
  - Section headings: 1.2rem (19.2px)
  - Navigation: 0.9rem (14.4px)
  - Body text: 0.9-1.1rem (14.4-17.6px)
  - Footer: 0.8rem (12.8px)

## Layout & Spacing
- **Container Width**: Maximum 800-1000px for content sections
- **Padding**: 
  - Header: 1.5rem 5%
  - Sections: 1.5-2rem
  - Cards: 1.5rem
- **Margins**:
  - Between sections: 4-5rem
  - Between elements: 1-2rem
- **Border Radius**: 8px for containers and cards
- **Line Height**: 1.6 for body text

## Background Elements
- **Star Background**: Subtle white dots on black background with 50% opacity
- **Gradient Overlay**: Very subtle radial gradient from center (almost imperceptible)
- **No Images**: The interface relies on typography and spacing rather than images

## UI Elements
- **Containers**: 
  - Dark gray backgrounds (rgba(18, 18, 18, 0.7))
  - Thin white borders (rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1))
  - Subtle box shadows for depth
- **Buttons**:
  - Transparent white background (rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1))
  - White text
  - No icons
  - Uppercase text
  - Hover effect: slightly lighter background
- **Input Fields**:
  - Dark background (rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3))
  - White text
  - No borders
  - Focus state: slightly darker background
- **Chat Messages**:
  - User messages: Light transparent background (rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1))
  - System messages: Dark background with white left border
  - Maximum width: 80% of container
  - Rounded corners with one flat corner

## Animation & Effects
- **Transitions**: Smooth 0.3s transitions for hover and focus states
- **Hover Effects**: 
  - Navigation: White underline animation
  - Buttons: Slightly lighter background
  - Feature cards: Subtle upward movement and shadow
- **Loading Animation**: White dots with pulsing animation

## Responsive Behavior
- **Breakpoint**: 768px for mobile adaptation
- **Mobile Adjustments**:
  - Stacked header elements
  - Reduced font sizes
  - Full-width feature cards
  - Reduced vertical spacing

## Important Style Rules
1. **No Icons**: Do not use any Material Icons or other icon fonts
2. **No Blue Colors**: Avoid all blue colors, including in gradients and accents
3. **Consistent Typography**: Use only Roboto Mono throughout the interface
4. **Uppercase for Navigation and Headings**: Maintain uppercase styling for these elements
5. **Minimalist Aesthetic**: Keep the interface clean and uncluttered
6. **White and Gray Only**: Stick to white and gray color variations for all elements

